0,304,238],"class_list":["post-25576","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-wisdom-al-hikmah","tag-ablution-wudu","tag-bathing-ghusl","tag-consensus-ijma","tag-drink-al-sharab","tag-fiqh","tag-imam-ash-shafiee","tag-insanity-al-junun","tag-major-impurity-al-junub","tag-medicine-al-tibb","tag-minor-impurity-al-hadath","tag-prayer-al-salat","tag-sleep-al-nawm","tag-wine-al-khamr"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-6Ew","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":25293,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/22\/when-the-prophet-forgot-ablution\/","url_meta":{"origin":25576,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Prayer: When the Prophet forgot ablution for prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The prayer had been prepared and the rows straightened, then the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, came out to us. When he stood in his place of prayer, he remembered that he was in a state of ritual impurity (junub). The Prophet said\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37042,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/09\/28\/prophets-ghusl-janabah\/","url_meta":{"origin":25576,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Ghusl: Description of the Prophet\u2019s ritual bath","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 28, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Maymunah reported: I brought water to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, for his ritual bath from major impurity. He washed his hands two or three times, then he put his right hand in the vessel and poured it over his private parts, washing it with\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13448,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/07\/method-ghusl-junub\/","url_meta":{"origin":25576,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ghusl: Performing ritual bath for major impurity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 7, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, took a ritual bath for major impurity, he began by washing his hands, then he would perform an ablution as if for prayer. Then, he would put his fingers in the water and wash the roots of his hair\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25581,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/07\/wudu-ablution-hadath-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":25576,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Ablution required before prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 7, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPrayer is not accepted from one in a state of minor impurity until he renews ablution.\u201d A man from Hadhramaut said, \u201cAbu Huraira, what is minor impurity?\u201d Abu Huraira said, \u201cIt is passing wind or gas.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15090,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/16\/junub-before-fasting\/","url_meta":{"origin":25576,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: Waking up in major impurity before fasting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 16, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would wake up at dawn in a state of major impurity, then he would perform a ritual bath and observe fasting. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1925, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1109 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25583,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/10\/wudu-nawm-junub\/","url_meta":{"origin":25576,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Perform ablution if sleeping with major impurity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 10, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: If the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, intended to sleep while in a state of major ritual impurity, he would perform ablution before he slept. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 282, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 305 Grade:\u00a0Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u